**We do not provide public support in this Discord.**
We provide limited private support to Patreon Patrons only.
You can become a Patron or find one of the many ESX support discords.
Continued support requests will result in warns or mutes.
We are doing this in order to focus on official development of ESX Reborn. 
You can find the ESX affiliated community Discord here: https://discord.gg/J6VqFPwvVp
